name: wavWRLD presents: wavROOM x Art Basel 2022

metadata.name: wavWRLD presents: wavROOM x Art Basel 2022
metadata.description: Welcome to a night of connection through intimate performances! The wavROOM experience allows artists and their true fans to come together for one-of-a-kind live concerts. You will also get to be a part of history, as these performances will be recorded and minted in collaboration with the artists post-event. You can mint a free ticket by being a collector of either Fred Riko, KarmaVioletta, FUTRxLGND, Lackhoney, or a collector of the previous wavROOM NFTs for the Art Basel wavROOM experience on December 1st.
